    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV72">
<l>cūḻkiṉṟa kaṅkuṟ curuṅkā viruḷiṉ karuntiṇimpaip</l>
<l>pōḻkiṉṟa tiṅkaḷam piḷḷaiyum pōḻka tuḻāymalarkkē</l>
<l>tāḻkiṉṟa neñcat torutami yāṭṭiyēṉ māmaikkiṉṟu</l>
<l>vāḻkiṉṟa vāṟitu vōvantu tōṉṟiṟṟu vāliyatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>a (= a new image of the moon as a ray of hope in the darkness)</l>
<l>The moon child too, that cuts across the black denseness of unshrinking darkness</l>
<l>in the surrounding night, let it cross. Is this the way to live on today</l>
<l>for the dark complexion of me, one solitary woman, with a heart low</l>
<l>because of the Tulsi blossoms? Something pure has turned up.</l>
<l></l>
<l>b (= the old topos of the moon that hinders the rendez-vous)</l>
<l>Let the moon child too be split, that splits the black denseness of unshrinking darkness</l>
<l>in the surrounding night. Is this the way to live on today</l> 
<l>for the dark complexion of me, one solitary woman, with a heart low</l>
<l>because of the Tulsi blossoms? Something white has turned up.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
